{"tid":19043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門要玩撚完???日本眾院委員會通過賭場法案!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-12-02T15:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T18:18:13.000Z","uid":10338,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2bdc604bea8015fdcc83e34a869911cff749c24","tid":19043,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】日本眾議院內閣委員會通過賭場法案，執政自民黨力推法案，本月獲國會正式通過。<br />\n<br />\n法案周四下午於在野民進黨議員強烈反對，並且退場抗議下表決。由於執政自民黨和日本維新黨議員佔多數，法案順利通過。<br />\n<br />\n以自民黨為首的執政聯盟在參眾兩院佔大多數議席，自民黨打算將法案交付眾議院全體會議下周二表決通過，繼而提交參議院，爭取在本月十四日國會會期結束前，正式通過法案。<br />\n<br />\n法案為日本興建賭場開綠燈，要求政府推動，建設以賭場為主的綜合度假區，在一年內進行必要的立法，同時加強對策應付嗜賭問題，支持者認為有助促進旅遊業，振興經濟。反對者批評開賭，是將發財建立在他人的不幸之上。"},{"pid":"657e755da6c597d10200c7eb43c55939a9926453","tid":19043,"uid":16447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人走撚曬最好"},{"pid":"1875c8728dd5a9c78753bf09681783a5668d495a","tid":19043,"uid":27772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70604dd824e0f87170881003c915a83f136767aa","tid":19043,"uid":14333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"唔好啊屌 我仲想去日本"},{"pid":"d1cdf45e6093af6cb720359d71e9a480ccd148b9","tid":19043,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"到時入到去又一班大陸妹問你去不去"},{"pid":"d1716037449b9b8262c28894829e58671829a25c","tid":19043,"uid":28353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"